  "text": "The strengths of my empirical approach are that it is model-free and that it can be applied to any portfolio of contingent claims, regardless of how difficult it is to value, and to any hedge instruments. The conditional method of moments developed in [CITATION_1] , and further extended in this paper, can therefore be used to examine multiperiod hedging of less stylized contingent claims.",
